      "description": "Like the mysterious cat, you are independent, observant, and possess a quiet wisdom. You value your autonomy and prefer to analyze situations before acting. Your intuitive nature helps you sense underlying truths that others miss. You maintain your own space and boundaries while still forming meaningful connections with those who understand your need for freedom.",
