    "dog": {
      "title": "The Loyal Protector",
      "description": "Your spirit resonates with the dog's unwavering loyalty and protective nature. You form deep bonds with those you care about and can be counted on in times of need. Your genuine approach to relationships makes you a trusted friend and ally. You value honesty and direct communication, and you're willing to stand up for what's right.",
      "characteristics": [
        "Steadfast loyalty",
